final_desc: - - Lain-lain :Minyak dan produk lainnya hasil penyulingan ter batu bara bersuhu tinggi; produk semacam itu yang berat unsur aromatiknya melebihi unsur non aromatik.;- - Other :Oils and other products of the distillation of high temperature coal tar; similar products in which the weight of the aromatic constituents exceeds that of the non-aromatic constituents.
